### GET all config values (including @Component AppInfo)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/config

### GET app name
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/config/app-name

### GET max items
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/config/max-items

### GET feature enabled status
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/config/feature-enabled

### GET app info from @Component
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/config/app-info